_sText:
TIME: 1600 Hours DATE: 3/6/2004 LOCATION: Somewhere in the mid-Atlantic The entire crew has been killed, slaughtered by Terrorists. Aboard the vessel is a small nuclear missile being shipped to an unknown destination. As one of the few people lucky to survive, you and the few of your colleagues left must defend the precious cargo by any means necessary . _____________________________________________ -FEATURES!- -32 Spawns. -Custom missile model complete with gibs and explosion sequence (courtesy of Black Sheep). -Soundscapes throughout the entire map. -HDR. -Bright sunny environments. _____________________________________________

Constructive feedback is appreciated as always :D
